  "description": "The MACRO KNOT sweeps dynamically via LFO1 at 0.22 Hz — topology shifts cyclically through the blend between Figure-Eight and Torus. At each crossing point (KNOT=0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0) the spectral character shifts. Saw strands make each crossing audible as a timbral event. The effect is a filter-like sweep but it is not a filter — it is the coupling matrix changing the relationships between oscillator strands. WEAVE-IV applied as motion: the chimera state passes through rather than rests in.",
